# Bazzite Gaming Optimization Suite Version Information
# Professional Gaming Suite - Advanced Features + Extended Platform Support

Version: 1.2.0
Release Name: "Professional Gaming Suite - Advanced Features + Extended Platform Support"
Release Date: 2025-11-18
Build: 14,500+ lines total (7,637 backend + ~2,600 GUI + ~4,300 advanced features)

# Key Components
Master Script: bazzite-optimizer.py (7,637 lines, 300KB)
GUI Application: bazzite-optimizer-gui.py (~2,500 lines)
GUI Modules: 16+ Python modules (models, controllers, UI components)
Advanced Features: Community, AI, Remote API (~1,500 lines)
Platform Support: Ubuntu/Debian, ROG Ally, Mobile APU (~1,800 lines)
Enhanced GUI: Historical graphs, profile editor, multi-GPU (~1,000 lines)
Restoration Tool: reset-bazzite-defaults.sh (Selective system restoration)
Security Framework: Enterprise-grade command injection protection
Optimizer Classes: 16 specialized optimization modules
Gaming Profiles: 4 built-in + unlimited custom profiles
Hardware Support: NVIDIA RTX + AMD RDNA2/RDNA3 + Intel + Mobile APUs
Platform Support: Bazzite, Fedora, Ubuntu, Debian, Arch, Steam Deck, ROG Ally

# Release Focus (v1.2.0) - Professional Gaming Suite

## Option A: GUI Enhancements
- **HISTORICAL METRICS GRAPHS**: matplotlib-based 5-minute historical graphs
- **CUSTOM PROFILE EDITOR**: Complete GUI editor for creating custom profiles
- **MULTI-GPU MANAGEMENT**: Support for NVIDIA + AMD + Intel hybrid configurations
- **SETTINGS PERSISTENCE**: Complete settings storage and recovery system

## Option B: Advanced Features
- **COMMUNITY PROFILE SHARING**: Upload/download custom profiles from community
- **CLOUD BENCHMARKING**: Compare performance with community database
- **AI-BASED AUTO-TUNING**: Intelligent profile recommendations and optimization
- **REMOTE MANAGEMENT API**: RESTful API for web-based control (port 8080)

## Option C: Platform Expansion
- **UBUNTU/DEBIAN SUPPORT**: Full optimization support for Ubuntu and Debian
- **ROG ALLY SUPPORT**: Complete handheld optimization for ASUS ROG Ally
- **MOBILE AMD APU OPTIMIZATION**: Battery-aware optimizations for mobile AMD APUs
- **MULTI-MONITOR PROFILES**: Per-monitor gaming configurations

## Technical Implementation
- Historical graphs with matplotlib integration
- JSON-based custom profile storage
- Multi-GPU detection and management
- Community features with local caching
- AI-based recommendation engine
- HTTP REST API server
- Platform-specific package managers (apt, rpm-ostree)
- Handheld TDP management
- Mobile power optimization
- Multi-monitor X11/Wayland integration

